  "guide": {
    "title": "Isikhokelo sokurekhoda i-Suno",
    "subtitle": "Indlela yokubamba ilizwi kunye negitare ithatha ezona ziphumo zibalaseleyo.",
    "intro": "I-Suno iqhuba kakuhle ngeembekiselo ezicocekileyo nezicacileyo. Esi sikhokelo sibandakanya amalungiselelo, amanqanaba ekujoliswe kuwo, kunye nescript semizuzu emi-3-5 yokurekhoda.",
    "sections": {
      "prep": {
        "title": "Ukulungiselela",
        "body": "Rekhoda kwigumbi eliphathwayo okanye enye enezinto ezininzi ezithambileyo (amakhethini, iiragi, iimpahla kwi-closet). Cima iifeni kunye nantoni na encwinayo. Lifudumeze ilizwi lakho imizuzu emi-5 phambi kokuba urekhode."
      },
      "levels": {
        "title": "Amanqanaba: -12 ukuya -6 dBFS",
        "body": "Injongo yeencopho phakathi kwe -12 kunye ne -6 dBFS kwimitha. Ngaphantsi kolo luhlu, ingxolo yangasemva ibonakala ngakumbi; ngaphezu kwayo, umngcipheko wokunqanda uyenyuka. Sebenzisa imitha kwiphepha leRekhodi ukuseta inzuzo yakho ngaphambi kokuba uqale."
      },
      "distance": {
        "title": "Umgama weMic: 15-30 cm",
        "body": "Hlala kwi-15 ukuya kwi-30 cm ukusuka kumakrofoni. Ikufutshane kunoko ibaxa iiplosives kunye neproximity effect; Kude lee uthatha isenzi segumbi kunye nengxolo."
      },
      "script": {
        "title": "Ukurekhoda umbhalo",
